Package nzilbb.ag.automation.util

Class Info

  • java.lang.Object
    • nzilbb.util.CommandLineProgram
      • nzilbb.ag.automation.util.Info
  • @ProgramDescription(value="Utility for displaying automatic annotator information",
                    arguments="class.or.jar")
public class Info
extends CommandLineProgram
    Utility for displaying annotator information.

    This can be run from the command like this:

    java -classpath nzilbb.ag.jar nzilbb.ag.automation.util.Info myjar.jar
